		title: Uruk Rager
		culture: isengard
		twilight: 4
		type: minion
		race: uruk-hai
		strength: 9
		vitality: 2
		site: 5
		keyword: damage+1
		effects: {
			type: Trigger
			optional: false
			trigger: {
				type: winsSkirmish
				filter: self
			}
			effect: {
				type: choice
				player: freeps
				texts: [
					Exert a companion
					Discard the top 3 cards of your draw deck
				]
				effects: [
					{
						type: exert
						select: choose(companion)
					}
					{
						type: discardTopCardsFromDeck
						deck: freeps
						count: 3
						forced: false
					}
				]
			}
		}
		gametext: <b>Damage +1</b>.<br>Each time this minion wins a skirmish, the Free Peoples player must exert a companion or discard the top 3 cards of their draw deck.
		lore: A bloodthirsty bellow from a huge Uruk can win a skirmish before it begins.
		promotext: ""
		alts: {
			promos: {
			}
			errata: {
			}
		}
	}
	
