		51_157: {
		cardInfo: {
			//id: 51_157.1
			parent: 1_157
			variant: ERRATA
			variantPath: errata/pc
			revision: 1
			image: errata/LOTR-EN01E157.1_card.jpg
			collInfo: 1C157
			rarity: C
		}
		title: Uruk-hai Armory
		unique: false
		side: Shadow
		culture: Isengard
		twilight: 1
		type: Condition
		keywords: Support Area
		effects: [
			{
				type: modifier
				modifier: {
					type: modifyArcheryTotal
					side: free people
					requires: {
						type: canSpot
						filter: uruk-hai
					}
					amount: -1
				}
			}
			{
				type: activated
				phase: shadow
				cost: {
					type: discard
					select: self
				}
				effect: {
					type: PlayCardFromDiscard
					select: choose(culture(isengard),possession)
				}
			}
			{
				type: Response
				trigger: {
					type: aboutToTakeWound
					filter: your,culture(isengard),minion
				}
				cost: [
					{
						type: removeTwilight
						amount: 1
					}
					{
						type: discard
						select: self
					}
				]
				effect: {
					type: preventWound
					select: choose(your,culture(isengard),minion)
				}
			}
		]
		gametext: While you can spot an Uruk-hai, the fellowship archery total is -1.<br><b>Shadow:</b> Discard this condition to play an [Isengard] possession from your discard pile.<br><b>Response:</b> If your [Isengard] minion is about to take a wound, remove (1) and discard this condition to prevent that wound.
		lore: ""
		promotext: ""
		alts: {
			promos: {
			}
			errata: {
			}
		}
	}
	
